HEADWORD: Retro-
<hw>Retro-</hw>. <ety>[L. <ets>retro</ets>, adv., backward, back. Cf.
<er>Re</er>-.]</ety> <def>A prefix or combining form signifying
<xex>backward</xex>, <xex>back</xex>; <as>as, <ex>retro</ex>act, to act
backward; <ex>retro</ex>spect, a looking back</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

